- content_for(:title, 'Vehicle is registered outside of the UK')
= link_to 'Back', enter_details_vehicle_checkers_path, class: 'govuk-back-link'

%main.govuk-main-wrapper#main-content{role: 'main'}
  .govuk-grid-row
    .govuk-grid-column-two-thirds
      %h1.govuk-heading-l Vehicle is registered outside of the UK
      %p
        We only hold data on UK-registered vehicles.
      %p
        Check your vehicle registration information against the national
        = link_to('standards',
                  'https://www.gov.uk/guidance/driving-in-a-clean-air-zone',
                  id: 'standards-link')
        and the zone you want to drive in. If your vehicle does not meet the standards, you need to pay a
        charge to drive in the Clean Air Zone.
      %p
        If you pay a charge in error, you may be able to claim a
        = link_to('refund',
                  'https://www.gov.uk/guidance/driving-in-a-clean-air-zone',
                  id: 'refund-link')
        from the local authority of the zone you drive in.
